# EmpireAI Beta (GB200 NVL72, aarch64) — cluster-scoped exports only. NO secret values
# (privileged values live in $DC_AGENT_SECRET_ENV = /mnt/home/bf996/secrets.env).
# HOME (/mnt/home/bf996, VAST, 100GB quota) is the primary code/config/cache area; large
# checkpoints/images belong on a DDN allocation (see .claude/ops/empireai/ops.md).
